http://www.cdc.gov/vhf/ebola/hcp/safety-training-course/training-toolkit.html

[Intended audience: Organizations that want to offer a training course for healthcare workers preparing to work in ETUs [Ebola treatment units] in Africa in response to the Ebola epidemic. A ProMED reader suggests these could equally be useful to hospitals in other countries wishing to prepare themselves for an imported case. - Mod.JW]

